{"tid":989714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"信德中心男子吊頸跳落水 當場不治","createTime":"2019-01-21T05:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T05:40:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf392e1dc5a77ed1c9a8b92be3b7a414a6299071","tid":989714,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"上環信德中心，今晨8時50分，一名男子被發現頸纏電線，吊在碼頭外。他滿頭白髮，穿著深色外套，下半身浸在水中，面向牆。消防員到場將他拉起，經救護員檢驗證實不治。警方初步相信他頸纏電線後，跨出欄杆跳落水，警方經調查後獲悉事主姓黎（68歲），於現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=mfnejbsFhuLinHjNFaGmHP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bc2bf975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190121/59165785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59165785&d=mfnejbsFhuLinHjNFaGmHP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3cea16de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59165785&h=998673cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190121/59165785</a>"},{"pid":"2f938826523a794c824e32b3c5627d721b1267b7","tid":989714,"uid":6752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"1日1年,1年都係死365人姐<br />\n只係數字黎"},{"pid":"743edcad470bf852668a035bd50d1ae67630f91d","tid":989714,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1日1件,1年都係死365人姐<br />\n只係數字黎</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8053d30b811e6dee938699f8003544868d5b0c5a","tid":989